*NB: before the start of the next season, it was revealed that Metalurg
*    had fixed their matches with Levski (Sofia) and Litex.  As punishment,
*    they were relegated, and Shumen kept their place.  Metalurg then merged
*    with Minjor.  Litex and Levski both had 3 points deducted.


